    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "そうだね。",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh man.",
      "zh": "喔，天哪。",
      "ja": "ああ、もう。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love this game.",
      "zh": "我喜歡這個遊戲。",
      "ja": "このゲームが大好きだ。",
      "time": "00:00:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's such great workout.",
      "zh": "這真的是很棒的運動。",
      "ja": "とても良い運動になる。",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All that running.",
      "zh": "一直跑來跑去。",
      "ja": "ずっと走り回るんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "そうだね。",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're pretty good for someone you never played before you came here.",
      "zh": "你對一個從沒玩過的人來說，表現得相當不錯。",
      "ja": "ここに来る前に一度もやったことがないのに、かなり上手だね。",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're very quick.",
      "zh": "你很快。",
      "ja": "君はとても速いね。",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Could you have a lot of moves?",
      "zh": "你會很多招式嗎？",
      "ja": "たくさんの動きができるの？",
      "time": "00:00:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh well, I think that comes from playing football.",
      "zh": "嗯，我想那是因為踢足球的關係。",
      "ja": "うーん、それはサッカーをやっていたからだと思う。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh you call a soccer for so long.",
      "zh": "嗯，你們叫它足球很久了。",
      "ja": "ええと、長い間サッカーと呼んでいるね。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There's a lot of running and the moves are similar.",
      "zh": "跑很多步，動作也很相似。",
      "ja": "たくさん走るし、動きも似ている。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But you get to use your hands in basketball.",
      "zh": "但籃球可以用手。",
      "ja": "でもバスケットボールは手を使うんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm wondering.",
      "zh": "我在想。",
      "ja": "ちょっと気になるんだけど。",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you know baseball, Lixie?",
      "zh": "你知道棒球嗎，Lixie？",
      "ja": "リクシー、野球は知ってる？",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh yes, I do.",
      "zh": "嗯，知道。",
      "ja": "うん、知ってるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I've never seen a real game because we don't have it in Greece.",
      "zh": "但我從沒看過真正的比賽，因為我們希臘沒有這項運動。",
      "ja": "でも本物の試合は見たことがない。ギリシャにはないから。",
      "time": "00:00:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Then let's watch the Yankees on TV this weekend.",
      "zh": "那這週末我們一起看洋基隊的比賽吧。",
      "ja": "じゃあ今週末、テレビでヤンキースの試合を見よう。",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I have cable TV in my apartment.",
      "zh": "我公寓有有線電視。",
      "ja": "僕のアパートにはケーブルテレビがある。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's great sport.",
      "zh": "這是很棒的運動。",
      "ja": "素晴らしいスポーツだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And we'll have a good night.",
      "zh": "我們會有個愉快的夜晚。",
      "ja": "楽しい夜になるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's a great idea.",
      "zh": "好主意。",
      "ja": "いい考えだね。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We have to play in the soon.",
      "zh": "我們很快也要打球。",
      "ja": "すぐにプレイしなきゃね。",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course, Angie will want to come too.",
      "zh": "當然，Angie也會想來。",
      "ja": "もちろん、アンジーも来たがるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She loves the Yankees.",
      "zh": "她很喜歡洋基隊。",
      "ja": "彼女はヤンキースが大好きだ。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well I will go tonight to see her this evening at her job.",
      "zh": "我今晚會去她工作的地方找她。",
      "ja": "今夜、彼女の仕事場に会いに行くよ。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will tell her then about our plan to see a baseball game.",
      "zh": "然後我會告訴她我們看棒球比賽的計畫。",
      "ja": "それから野球観戦の計画を伝えるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have a nice day.",
      "zh": "祝你有美好的一天。",
      "ja": "良い一日を。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Angie, good to see you.",
      "zh": "Angie，很高興見到你。",
      "ja": "アンジー、会えて嬉しいよ。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, guess what?",
      "zh": "嘿，你猜怎麼著？",
      "ja": "ねえ、聞いて。",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There's a Yankees match this Saturday night.",
      "zh": "這週六晚上有洋基隊的比賽。",
      "ja": "今週の土曜の夜にヤンキースの試合があるんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Jack Sam and I want to watch it at Jack's apartment.",
      "zh": "Jack、Sam和我想在Jack的公寓看。",
      "ja": "ジャック、サムと僕はジャックのアパートで見たいんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can you come with us?",
      "zh": "你能和我們一起去嗎？",
      "ja": "一緒に来られる？",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love seeing the Yankees play.",
      "zh": "我喜歡看洋基隊比賽。",
      "ja": "ヤンキースの試合を見るのが大好き。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But I think I have to work that night.",
      "zh": "但我想那晚我得工作。",
      "ja": "でもその夜は仕事かもしれない。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe I could ask Donna to switch nights with me.",
      "zh": "也許我可以請Donna替我換班。",
      "ja": "ドナに夜勤を代わってもらえるか聞いてみよう。",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me see.",
      "zh": "讓我看看。",
      "ja": "ちょっと見てみる。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Donna, can you work for me this Saturday?",
      "zh": "Donna，你這週六能替我上班嗎？",
      "ja": "ドナ、今週の土曜に代わってくれる？",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think that I can.",
      "zh": "我想我可以。",
      "ja": "できると思う。",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm off and could use the money.",
      "zh": "我休假，可以賺點錢。",
      "ja": "休みだし、お金が欲しいからね。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What time do you start?",
      "zh": "你幾點開始上班？",
      "ja": "何時から？",
      "time": "00:02:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The schedule says I'm on at 7 p.m.",
      "zh": "排班表說我晚上七點上班。",
      "ja": "スケジュールでは午後7時からだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can you be there then?",
      "zh": "那時你能到嗎？",
      "ja": "その時間に行ける？",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, I should take the night off and just rest because I've been working so much.",
      "zh": "嗯，我應該休息一晚，因為我工作太多了。",
      "ja": "うーん、たくさん働いてるから夜は休みたいな。",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But I want to take a vacation and travel Europe next year.",
      "zh": "但我想明年去歐洲度假旅行。",
      "ja": "でも来年ヨーロッパ旅行に行きたいんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I should save some money now.",
      "zh": "我現在應該存點錢。",
      "ja": "今はお金を貯めなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So yes.",
      "zh": "所以好吧。",
      "ja": "だから、うん。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll work for you this Saturday.",
      "zh": "這週六我會替你上班。",
      "ja": "今週の土曜は代わるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wonderful, Donna.",
      "zh": "太好了，Donna。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい、ドナ。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So Alexey, it looks like I can come with you guys.",
      "zh": "所以Alexey，看起來我可以跟你們一起去。",
      "ja": "じゃあアレクセイ、君たちと一緒に行けそうだね。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We'll have a fun time.",
      "zh": "我們會玩得很開心。",
      "ja": "楽しい時間になるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Alexey, wait a minute.",
      "zh": "Alexey，等一下。",
      "ja": "アレクセイ、ちょっと待って。",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I know that you could play football and you could play basketball now.",
      "zh": "我知道你會踢足球，也會打籃球。",
      "ja": "君はサッカーもバスケットボールもできるね。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But can you play baseball?",
      "zh": "但你會打棒球嗎？",
      "ja": "でも野球はできる？",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不會。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I've never played baseball before.",
      "zh": "我從沒打過棒球。",
      "ja": "野球は一度もやったことがない。",
      "time": "00:02:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want to learn how to play the game.",
      "zh": "我想學打這個遊戲。",
      "ja": "このゲームのやり方を覚えたい。",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And Sam and Jack thought, I should see a game.",
      "zh": "Sam和Jack覺得我應該去看場比賽。",
      "ja": "サムとジャックは、試合を見たほうがいいと言った。",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They also said it'd be a lot of fun.",
      "zh": "他們也說會很有趣。",
      "ja": "それにとても楽しいって。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They're right.",
      "zh": "他們說得對。",
      "ja": "その通りだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Seeing the Yankees play on the summer night is a great experience.",
      "zh": "在夏夜看洋基隊比賽是很棒的體驗。",
      "ja": "夏の夜にヤンキースの試合を見るのは素晴らしい経験だ。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I bring my little brothers?",
      "zh": "我可以帶我弟弟們一起去嗎？",
      "ja": "弟たちを連れて行ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They talk about baseball all the time.",
      "zh": "他們一直在談論棒球。",
      "ja": "彼らはいつも野球の話をしている。",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "可以。",
      "ja": "いいよ。",
      "time": "00:03:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is fine with me if you bring your little brothers.",
      "zh": "如果你帶弟弟們來，我沒問題。",
      "ja": "弟たちを連れてきても僕は構わない。",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But you should ask Sam and Jack too.",
      "zh": "但你也應該問問Sam和Jack。",
      "ja": "でもサムとジャックにも聞いたほうがいいよ。",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good idea.",
      "zh": "好主意。",
      "ja": "いい考えだ。",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll call them and see what they say.",
      "zh": "我會打電話給他們看看他們怎麼說。",
      "ja": "電話して彼らの返事を聞くよ。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "See you later.",
      "zh": "回頭見。",
      "ja": "またね。",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "再見。",
      "ja": "バイバイ。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello?",
      "zh": "喂？",
      "ja": "もしもし？",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey Sam, it's me, Alexey.",
      "zh": "嘿Sam，是我，Alexey。",
      "ja": "やあサム、アレクセイだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, what's up?",
      "zh": "嘿，怎麼了？",
      "ja": "やあ、どうした？",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can you come to watch the game this Saturday?",
      "zh": "你這週六能來看比賽嗎？",
      "ja": "今週の土曜に試合を見に来られる？",
      "time": "00:03:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, I can.",
      "zh": "可以，我能去。",
      "ja": "うん、行けるよ。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And Angie can come too.",
      "zh": "Angie也能來。",
      "ja": "アンジーも来られる。",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Excellent.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, I have a question.",
      "zh": "嘿，我有個問題。",
      "ja": "ねえ、質問があるんだけど。",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I bring my brothers along with us?",
      "zh": "我可以帶我弟弟們一起去嗎？",
      "ja": "弟たちも一緒に連れて行っていい？",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They've never seen a game either.",
      "zh": "他們也從沒看過比賽。",
      "ja": "彼らも試合を見たことがないんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I think they would love baseball.",
      "zh": "我覺得他們會喜歡棒球。",
      "ja": "野球を気に入ると思う。",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's fine with me.",
      "zh": "我沒問題。",
      "ja": "僕は構わないよ。",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They'll have a great time.",
      "zh": "他們會玩得很開心。",
      "ja": "楽しい時間を過ごせるよ。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Should I ask Jack or do you think he will be okay with them coming along with us?",
      "zh": "我該問Jack嗎？你覺得他會同意他們一起來嗎？",
      "ja": "ジャックに聞いたほうがいい？彼らが来るのは大丈夫かな？",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think you should ask him if they can come over.",
      "zh": "我覺得你應該問他他們能不能來。",
      "ja": "彼らが来てもいいかジャックに聞いたほうがいいよ。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He's planning to ask some friends.",
      "zh": "他正打算邀請一些朋友。",
      "ja": "彼は友達を何人か呼ぶ予定だ。",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "そうだね。",
      "time": "00:04:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We should be sure that there's enough room for everyone.",
      "zh": "我們應該確定有足夠的空間給大家。",
      "ja": "みんなが入れる十分なスペースがあるか確認しよう。",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good idea.",
      "zh": "好主意。",
      "ja": "いい考えだ。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll call him right now.",
      "zh": "我現在就打給他。",
      "ja": "今すぐ電話するよ。",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:04:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "再見。",
      "ja": "バイバイ。",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "再見。",
      "ja": "バイバイ。",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello?",
      "zh": "喂？",
      "ja": "もしもし？",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Jack.",
      "zh": "Jack。",
      "ja": "ジャック。",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Alexey here.",
      "zh": "我是Alexey。",
      "ja": "アレクセイだよ。",
      "time": "00:04:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How are you?",
      "zh": "你好嗎？",
      "ja": "元気？",
      "time": "00:04:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, great.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "うん、元気だよ。",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And you?",
      "zh": "你呢？",
      "ja": "君は？",
      "time": "00:04:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm okay.",
      "zh": "我還好。",
      "ja": "僕は大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:04:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm with Angie.",
      "zh": "我和Angie在一起。",
      "ja": "アンジーと一緒だよ。",
      "time": "00:04:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I asked Angie about the baseball game.",
      "zh": "我問了Angie關於棒球比賽的事。",
      "ja": "アンジーに野球の試合について聞いた。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She can come.",
      "zh": "她可以來。",
      "ja": "彼女は来られるって。",
      "time": "00:04:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have a question for you.",
      "zh": "我有個問題想問你。",
      "ja": "質問があるんだ。",
      "time": "00:04:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can my little brothers come to your flat too?",
      "zh": "我弟弟們也能來你家嗎？",
      "ja": "弟たちも君の家に来てもいい？",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's fine with me.",
      "zh": "我沒問題。",
      "ja": "僕は構わないよ。",
      "time": "00:04:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think they'll have a great time.",
      "zh": "我覺得他們會玩得很開心。",
      "ja": "彼らは楽しい時間を過ごせると思う。",
      "time": "00:04:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:04:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks for letting them come.",
      "zh": "謝謝你讓他們來。",
      "ja": "彼らを来させてくれてありがとう。",
      "time": "00:04:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't wait to tell them they're going to watch the Yankees play.",
      "zh": "我迫不及待想告訴他們他們要去看洋基隊比賽了。",
      "ja": "彼らにヤンキースの試合を見るって伝えるのが待ちきれない。",
      "time": "00:04:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No problem.",
      "zh": "沒問題。",
      "ja": "問題ないよ。",
      "time": "00:05:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See you tomorrow.",
      "zh": "明天見。",
      "ja": "また明日。",
      "time": "00:05:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:05:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "See you later.",
      "zh": "回頭見。",
      "ja": "またね。",
      "time": "00:05:03"
    }
  ]
}